It is no longer news that the alleged 15-year-old boy at the center of Ike Ekweremadu Saga has been identified to be David Ukpo. 

It would be recalled that the former senate president and his wife were put on detention over alleged human organ trafficking. The couple also appeared before a court in the United Kingdom.
More revelations has been emerging concerning the identity of the boy whom is said to have been taken to the United Kingdom by the couple in order to harvest his kidney for their daughter
As Nigerians await the outcome of the court case on the issue, an old Tiktok Video of David Ukpo made its way to the social media.
In the video, David Ukpo is heard stating that he owns six bank accounts but he doesn’t have even upto 1k in them. He also said he would deal with the situation.
Meanwhile, Nigerians have been reacting over the video clip. Check out some of the comments after the cut.



